    <item>
      <title>Crypto&#39;s Real Design Problem Is Not Usability</title>
      <link>https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-this-conversation&#34;&gt;About This Conversation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A conversation with Kyle Becker about crypto UX (user experience), institutional finance, and why blockchain design needs to focus on systems strategy.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;AI (artificial intelligence)-readable JSON (JavaScript Object Notation): &lt;a href=&#34;https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/conversation.json&#34;&gt;https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/conversation.json&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;AI-readable JSON: &lt;a href=&#34;https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/conversation.json&#34;&gt;https://nefko.xyz/blog/conversations/crypto-industry-today/conversation.json&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;conversation&#34;&gt;Conversation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;turn-001&#34;&gt;Herb&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Kyle, in your earlier crypto work, including the &lt;a href=&#34;https://nefko.xyz/case-studies/cradl-ux-in-cryptocurrency/&#34;&gt;UX (user experience) in Cryptocurrency report&lt;/a&gt; and your essay on &lt;a href=&#34;https://nefko.xyz/blog/my-custom-url/&#34;&gt;Web3 in 2023&lt;/a&gt;, you seemed to argue that crypto’s real bottleneck was not merely bad UX, but unclear usefulness once speculation was removed. Now, in 2026, the industry looks more mature on the surface: stablecoins are closer to regulated payment infrastructure, account abstraction has softened some of the old wallet pain, ETFs (exchange-traded funds) have made crypto legible to institutions, and banks are absorbing parts of the stack.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Institutional assets on-chain at J.P. Morgan.</title>
      <link>https://nefko.xyz/case-studies/jpm-onyx/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://nefko.xyz/case-studies/jpm-onyx/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I was super excited to see J.P. Morgan and Blackrock&amp;rsquo;s public announcement about their on-chain collateral management pilot.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I worked on the interface for the initial pilot of this product during my time with J.P. Morgan Onyx—the company&amp;rsquo;s blockchain-focused division. This particular project solved a major (and expensive) painpoint for complex trading organizations: collateral management.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA; &#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block {&#xA; &#xA;  box-sizing: border-box;&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__card {&#xA; &#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: row;&#xA;  align-items: flex-start;&#xA;  gap: 1.5rem;&#xA;  box-sizing: border-box;&#xA;  margin: 2rem;&#xA;  padding: 1rem;&#xA;  background-color: var(--bg-inverse-primary);&#xA;  box-shadow: var(--shadow-callout-block);&#xA;  border-radius: 1px;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block :is(.p-sm, .p-sm-heavy) {&#xA;  padding-top: 0;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__photo-wrap {&#xA;  flex-shrink: 0;&#xA;  width: 4.5rem;&#xA;  height: 11.5rem;&#xA;  overflow: hidden;&#xA;  box-shadow: var(--shadow-callout-block);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__photo {&#xA;  display: block;&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;  height: 100%;&#xA;  object-fit: cover;&#xA;  object-position: center top;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__content {&#xA;  flex: 1;&#xA;  min-width: 0;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: column;&#xA;  gap: 1.5rem;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__quotes {&#xA;  margin: 0;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: column;&#xA;  gap: 0.375rem;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__big-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__small-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__name,&#xA;.testimonial-block__title,&#xA;.testimonial-block__company {&#xA;  margin: 0;&#xA;  color: var(--text-inverse-primary);&#xA;  text-align: left;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.serif .testimonial-block__big-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__big-quote {&#xA