;&#xA;          &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__photo-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;img class=&#34;testimonial-block__photo&#34;&#xA;                 src=&#34;https://nefko.xyz/images/testimonial-avatars/Lawrence-Lipkin.jpeg&#34;&#xA;                 alt=&#34;Lawrence Lipkin&#34;&#xA;                 loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;          &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__quotes&#34;&gt;&#xA;              &lt;p class=&#34;testimonial-block__big-quote serif-display&#34;&gt;able to learn complex domains quickly, and uses his superb story-telling skills to re-shape and re-frame business ideas into cohesive narratives that enable cross-functional teams to collaborate more effectively.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
